<div class="banner" >
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Read List helps all bookworms!</h1>
    <p>Record your precious reading history.</p>
    <%= link_to "Get Started", list_path, class:"btn btn-primary" %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-s">
  <div class="content">
    <h1 class="text-center">About</h1>
    <div class="content-about">
      <p>Even though I read a lot of books, I forgot how many I've read...</p>
      <p>I should have had a lot of impressions, but I forgot my impressions with time...</p>
      <h3 class="text-center">Read List is an app that solves these problems that bookworms have.</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h1 class="text-center">Features</h1>
    <div class="contents">
      <div class="content-feature">
        <h2>- List</h2>
        <h3>Manage your reading progress</h3>
        <div class="img-box">
          <%= image_tag "progress.png"%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-feature">
        <h2>- Books</h2>
        <h3>Your book list with your reviews</h3>
        <div class="img-box">
          <%= image_tag "index.png"%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-feature">
        <h2>- Calendar</h2>
        <h3>Check your reading schedules</h3>
        <div class="img-box">
          <%= image_tag "calendar.png"%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-feature">
        <h2>- Analytics</h2>
        <h3>Check your reading history</h3>
        <div class="img-box">
          <%= image_tag "analytics.png"%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
